00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:14.820
New York-en hazi nintzen

00:00:14.820 --> 00:00:17.080
Harlem eta Bronx auzoen artean.

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:18.820
Mutil izanda, irakatsi ziguten

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:20.820
gizonok gogor eta indartsu

00:00:20.820 --> 00:00:23.820
ausart eta menderatzaile
izan behar genuela,

00:00:23.820 --> 00:00:26.580
minik gabe, emoziorik gabe

00:00:26.580 --> 00:00:27.820
amorrua izan ezik,

00:00:27.820 --> 00:00:30.040
eta, batez ere, beldurrik gabe;

00:00:30.570 --> 00:00:31.820
Gizonok agintzen dugula,

00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:33.710
hots, emakumeek ez.

00:00:33.710 --> 00:00:35.820
Gizonok bideratzen dugula

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:38.820
eta, guk esaten duguna egin behar duzuela.

00:00:38.820 --> 00:00:41.820
Gizonok goi-mailakoak garela;
emakumeak, behe-mailakoak.

00:00:41.820 --> 00:00:44.820
Gizonok indartsuak garela; emakumeak ahulak.

00:00:45.970 --> 00:00:47.820
Emakumeek gutxiago balio dutela,

00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:50.490
