00:03:17.820 --> 00:03:19.820
Eta gogoratu nuen.

00:03:19.820 --> 00:03:22.820
Nire aita gogoratu nuen.

00:03:22.820 --> 00:03:24.820
Nire bizitzaren garai batean,

00:03:24.820 --> 00:03:27.820
oso esperientzia traumatikoa
jasan genuen familian.

00:03:27.820 --> 00:03:30.080
Nire anaia Henry tragikoki hil egin zen

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.820
